## Browser API Capabilities Matrix

### Chrome Bookmarks API

**Documentation:** [chrome.bookmarks API reference](https://developer.chrome.com/docs/extensions/reference/api/bookmarks)

**Permission Required:** `"bookmarks"` in manifest.json

**Key Methods:**
| Method | Purpose | Notes |
|--------|---------|-------|
| `bookmarks.getTree()` | Retrieves entire bookmark hierarchy | Returns BookmarkTreeNode root |
| `bookmarks.getChildren(id)` | Get children of folder | For folder iteration |
| `bookmarks.create(bookmark)` | Create bookmark/folder | Can specify parent folder |
| `bookmarks.update(id, changes)` | Modify bookmark | Title and URL only |
| `bookmarks.move(id, destination)` | Relocate bookmark | Change parent or index |
| `bookmarks.remove(id)` | Delete bookmark | Cannot remove root folders |
| `bookmarks.removeTree(id)` | Recursively delete folder | Use with caution |
| `bookmarks.search(query)` | Find bookmarks | Searches title and URL |
| `bookmarks.getRecent(n)` | Get n recent bookmarks | Useful for "what's new" |

**Event Listeners:**
- `bookmarks.onCreated` - Fires when bookmark added
- `bookmarks.onRemoved` - Fires when bookmark deleted
- `bookmarks.onChanged` - Fires when title/URL updated
- `bookmarks.onMoved` - Fires when bookmark relocated
- `bookmarks.onImportBegan/Ended` - Import detection

**Limitations:**
- Cannot modify root folder
- Cannot rename/move "Bookmarks Bar" or "Other Bookmarks" special folders
- Update events only fire for title and URL changes (not folder changes)
- Write operation rate limits removed in 2025 (was a previous limitation)

**Manifest V3 Status:** ✅ Fully supported, no breaking changes from V2

**Sources:**
- [API reference | Chrome for Developers](https://developer.chrome.com/docs/extensions/reference/api)
- [chrome.bookmarks | API | Chrome for Developers](https://developer.chrome.com/docs/extensions/reference/api/bookmarks)

