### Firefox Bookmarks API

**Documentation:** [Work with the Bookmarks API - Mozilla | MDN](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Work_with_the_Bookmarks_API)

**Cross-Browser Compatibility:** ✅ Based on Chrome's `chrome.bookmarks` API

